Commands for inspecting and operating the bundled mcp-sentinel analytics, gateway, and observability stack.

Usage:
  mcp-runtime sentinel [command]

Available Commands:
  events       Show recent Kubernetes events for mcp-sentinel
  logs         View logs for a mcp-sentinel component
  port-forward Port-forward a common mcp-sentinel service
  restart      Restart one or all mcp-sentinel workloads
  status       Show mcp-sentinel stack status

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for sentinel

Global Flags:
      --debug   Enable debug mode with structured error logging

Use "mcp-runtime sentinel [command] --help" for more information about a command.
